doctype html
html
  include ../layout/head.pug
    
  body
    include ../layout/navigation.pug
    
    header.index
      #particles-js
      h1 SPACE-X
      
      //- #index-header acts as a array of strings which typed.js uses for the animation and will not be visible
      #index-header
        h2 Making Life 
        h2 Multiplanetary
      //- #index-header-typed is where typed.js inserts the animated string
      span#index-header-typed
      
      a(href="#mars-article")
        include ../components/scroll-down-icon.pug
    
    section.index
      article#mars-article
        h2 MARS:
        h3 Picturesque and <br> closer than ever
        p In 2022 our spacecraft BFR (Big Falcon Rocket) will head towards the Red Planet, Mars. As of today only 18 missions have been successful, however, we are about to change that. In 2022 our spacecraft filled with cargo is ready for take-off, with a mission to establish resources and sort out initial power, mining and infrastructure. <br><br> 2024 is the year our spacecraft will include people, alongside cargo. This time, to build a propellant depot and our first base on Mars. We are now preparing for a future cosmopolitan society on our neighbour, the Red Planet.
        button(type="button" onclick="location.href='bfr.html';" value="Go to the big falcon rocket info page")
          h4 More about BFR
      
        .video-container  
          iframe(width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ndpxuf-uJHE?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen)
        
      #newsletter-signup
        h2 Get updated
        h3 Recieve our newsletter
        form(onsubmit="return false")#my-form
          label(for="email") @
          input(type="email" placeholder="Enter email" name="email" pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,4}$" required)#email-input
          button(type="submit" onclick="formValidation()")#submit SUBMIT
          
        .video-container  
          iframe(width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ndpxuf-uJHE?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen)
      
